WEBVTT

00:14:29.263 --> 00:14:30.413
Zašto?

00:14:30.437 --> 00:14:32.264
Zato što morate tražiti pomoć.

00:14:38.959 --> 00:14:40.347
Slomljeno srce.

00:14:40.371 --> 00:14:42.483
Nemamo izbora oko slomljenog srca,

00:14:42.507 --> 00:14:46.482
imamo samo izbor
da nam srce slome

00:14:46.506 --> 00:14:51.936
ljudi i stvari i projekti
za koje marimo.

00:14:53.404 --> 00:14:55.472
A zadnja je iluzija

00:14:55.496 --> 00:14:59.933
da mogu dovoljno planirati i organizirati

00:14:59.957 --> 00:15:03.572
tako da vidim cestu do kraja